All code is written using Python 3.9 in addition to pyspark.

1)  Make sure that a map Data is created in the same folder as were Main.py is saved.
2)  add the file sp500_stocks.csv to this Data map.
    This can be found by following the link given in the dataset description of Chapter 4 of this Thesis
3)  Install all packages that are used in this project.
4)  Run Main.py, uncommeting the code snippet that belongs to the experiment that you want to verify.
    These code snippet are found in def execution, including a description of their parameters.

